"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ouch, my hair!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1098
msgid ""
"That was painful.\n"
"She pulled out my hair."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1099
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Ow!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1100
msgid "Rin pulled out a few strands of her own hair. Her hair was so long that it almost touched the floor. Despite the differences in length, Rin tied our hair together."
