"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Are you all right? Are you hurt?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1129
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I'm all right.\n"
"What was I doing?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1130
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's what I want to know.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1134
msgid "*fsssshhhhhh*"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1135
msgid ""
"The fire in the pot was going out.\n"
"Now it's as small as my little finger.\n"
"And finally..."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1136
msgid "The fire went out completely."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1139
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hey, the fire just went out! Isn't that bad?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1140
msgid "I thought that our only reason for being here was to keep it burning."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1143
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"It's OK. We've done our time.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1144
msgid "Haruka pointed to an hourglass in the corner. All of the sand had fallen from the top, showing that we had indeed served our time."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1145
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I see. It's over.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1146
msgid ""
"Everyone felt so relieved.\n"
"Right at that moment......"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1149
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What's that?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1150
msgid "The atmosphere regained its intensity."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1151
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What is it this time?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1154
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"T-t-that!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1155
msgid "Haruka's voice was shaking. Her eyes were as wide as saucers yet she focused on one tiny point."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1156
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What the... WOW!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1160
msgid "There was a little girl inside the glass flask over the furnace."
