"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Wow, a girl in a bottle?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1165
msgid "Sakura was sitting up from the floor and staring in disbelief. Nobody, including myself, could find anything to say."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1166
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"What in the world have we created?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1167
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"What's that?\n"
"Who's the pedo?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1168
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Huh? The fire's out?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1169
msgid "Everybody started regaining consciousness one by one. They took a closer look at what emerged from the fire."
