#: 02606:1170
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"What happened to us?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1171
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"We must have fallen asleep. But how?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1172
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Are we done? What on earth is that?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1173
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................Haruma. Haruma.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1174
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What? Me?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1175
msgid ""
"The little girl in the bottle was calling to me.\n"
"How does she know my name?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1176
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Let me out! Quick!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1177
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh, sorry.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1178
msgid "It looked very tight inside the bottle. We should let her out of the flask at least."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1179
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Who is it? Do you know her?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1180
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No, I don't.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1181
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Then, how come she knows your name?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1182
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"You must have hit on her somewhere before.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1183
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"You were so persistent, she had to hit you and you lost your memory or something.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1184
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Kazushi-kun, are you that persistent?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1185
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't believe them.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1186
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I don't know what's going on either, but right now, we should let her out from there.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1187
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Haruma, hurry up.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1188
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I'm on it.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1189
msgid "I guess I have no choice but to break the bottle.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1193
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Sure. Go ahead and break it.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1195
msgid "After Haruka caught my hesitation and urged me on, I carefully broke the huge flask."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1199
msgid "From the cracks, her arms and legs unfolded as she reached for me."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1202
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Pull.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1203
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Sure.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1204
msgid "I grabbed her tiny hands and pulled her from the wreckage. She was as light as a fairy."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1207
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Phew... I messed up a bit.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1208
msgid "She stretched out and looked around."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1213
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Umm, who are you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1214
msgid ""
"Haruka went up to greet her.\n"
"The girl looked over at Haruka."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1217
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Umm...?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1218
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Are you Hisae's granddaughter?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1221
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What? You know my grandma?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1224
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Tell her I said she's an ugly bitch!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1225
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What? Ugly?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1226
msgid "She's got a foul mouth, even though she looks like a cute little girl."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1231
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Hey, guys, are we done with our assignment?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1232
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yeah, are we?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1236
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Yes, you are. You guys are free to go.\n"
"Haruma, come with me.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1237
msgid "She pulled my arm."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1238
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh? S-sure... Hey, how do you know my name?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1244
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Kazushi's quick to get along with little girls.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1245
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"'Cause he's a lolicon.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1249
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Huh?! No way?!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1253
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Wait, really? That's creepy.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1254
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"They're joking. Please don't believe them.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1259
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Come on, hurry up.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1260
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"All right, all right. Don't pull me so hard.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1261
msgid "I'd really like to know who this girl is."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1268
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"Good work, everyone.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1269
msgid "We were all summoned to the principal's office."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1273
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1274
msgid "The girl from the bottle was there with us too. Again she was wearing an unhappy face."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1279
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"I never expected you to come out and bother us.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1280
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1281
msgid ""
"She's ignoring the principal.\n"
"Was she even listening to her to begin with?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1282
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hey you.\n"
"Do you know the principal is talking to you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1285
msgid "She glared back at me."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1288
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Haruma, give her my answer for me. I have nothing to say to that woman.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1289
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That woman......\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1290
msgid "Who does this girl think she is, calling the principal 'that woman'? And why does she know my name?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1291
msgid "I don't think we've met before..."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1294
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Hmph...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1295
msgid "I felt her hostility towards me as well..."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1296
msgid "Did I do something wrong to her?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1299
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"This is Amamiya Natsume-san. She's a first year. Everyone, please be nice to her.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1302
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1305
msgid "Natsume-chan looked away as the principal introduced her to us. The principal smiled bitterly."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1306
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"Don't worry. I'll think of how to handle her later.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1307
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1308
msgid "Who is this girl, and what is she to the principal? How did she appear here?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1311
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"Good job, everybody. You accomplished your task splendidly. As I promised, there will be no further penalties regarding last week's incident.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1315
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"Really?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1318
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"Absolutely. After all, that was the promise.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1322
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"Did you hear that, Rei?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1323
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"Thank you, guys. It's all thanks to your help.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1324
msgid "Andou's sensitive tears belied her huge body."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1329
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Look at the giantess crying.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1330
msgid "This must have been quite an interesting scene for her to witness. Amamiya Natsume-chan, huh? What a strange girl."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1331
msgid "Even though we saved ourselves from getting kicked out of school again, I didn't feel like we'd managed to accomplish anything."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1332
msgid "I'm sure I'm not the only one who feels that way either."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1343
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Hi, Natsume-chan! You're very pretty! It's nice to meet you!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1346
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"You're adorable.\n"
"I want to be your big sister.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1347
msgid "Everybody gathered around Natsume-chan as soon as we left the principal's office."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1351
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Do your parents happen to be rich?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1352
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1353
msgid "She looked at us with confusion in her eyes as we greeted her."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1358
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Haruma.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1359
msgid "Natsume-chan left the circle and hid behind me."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1360
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What's wrong?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1363
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I want you to beat them up for me, Haruma.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1364
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What? Why?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1367
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"It's not that I'm scared.\""
