#: 02606:1368
msgid "She was shaking a bit. I guess she was afraid. Maybe she's not used to people?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1369
msgid "She seemed arrogant, but maybe she's just extra shy?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1373
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"What's wrong? Are we scaring you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1374
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"This is your fault, Ran. Who brings up money as soon as she meets somebody?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1377
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"You're saying that I've creeped her out? No way. It's only natural to enquire about assets when choosing your friends.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1382
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No it's not.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1389
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Look at her, she's so delicate.\n"
"She's peering out at us from behind Haruma-kun.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1392
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Keep watching me and you'll be cursed.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1395
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"What!? Why?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1396
msgid "Natsume-chan almost made Fujisaki-san cry. Yeah, despite her appearance, Natsume-chan is just extremely shy."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1401
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"Hey guys, that's enough.\n"
"You need to get back to class - you've still got exams today.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1402
msgid "Mei-sensei's words froze us in our tracks."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1410
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"What? We've still got exams today?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1411
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Without any chance to rest?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1412
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"I'm really tired. We hardly slept last night.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1413
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I didn't even study!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1417
msgid "Everyone here couldn't wait to go back to the dorm to sleep."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1420
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"I'm sorry about this, too, but last night was only your penalty. You're young though, so just work hard for one day.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1424
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Oh no! It's going to be a long day.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1425
msgid "Everybody's exhaustion was catching up with them. I can't believe we have to keep taking our exams now."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1431
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"Amamiya-san, you stay here. I'm going to show you to your dorm.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1434
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1437
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"Amamiya-san?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1438
msgid "Natsume-chan seemed to have a habit of staring directly into peoples' faces."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1439
msgid "Right now, she's staring at Mei-sensei and perplexing her."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1442
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Interesting.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1445
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"What?\n"
"What's so interesting about my face?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1448
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"It's a secret.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1451
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"What is it...?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1452
msgid "Mei-sensei's face was scrunched up in annoyance."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1453
msgid "Wow, she's even got the power to disturb the teachers."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1457
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Haruma, come visit my room later on.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1458
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me? You want me to come to your room?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1459
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Sure.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1460
msgid "She's already inviting me to her room!"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1465
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"Of course he's not coming to your room! Boys aren't permitted to enter the girls' dorm.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1466
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Of course. That's what I thought.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1467
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"That's fine. You can come.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1470
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"That's not going to happen. Here, let's go.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1473
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Hey, don't you pull my arm like that! It'll stretch!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1476
msgid "Mei-sensei escorted Natsume-chan into the dorm like a prisoner under a policeman's guard."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1483
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"She's so cute!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1484
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"I wanna abduct her so we can take our baths together!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1487
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"You need to choose your words more carefully before you speak.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1491
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Kazushi-kun, are you SURE you haven't met her before?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1492
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I don't think so...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1496
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"But she's already become awfully attached to you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1504
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"That's 'cause Kazushi emits an aura that just makes lolis swoon.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1505
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Oh yeah! Hey, remember the time...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1506
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No, no, no, there is no such aura. And can you please stop saying things that might lead to trouble in these times?!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1511
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1512
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't look at me like I'm a criminal!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1513
msgid "I still can't figure out how she knows my name."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1519
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"It's the bell. Let's go.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1520
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Get ready for a long day.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1521
msgid "It's going to be one hell of a long day."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1529
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I'm dog tired.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1530
msgid "Our long day was finally coming to a close."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1531
msgid "We took our baths, came back to the dorm, and collapsed on our beds."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1532
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I'm so sleepy after that all-nighter.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1533
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What are you talking about? You got to sleep last night! I'm actually feeling kind of awake though.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1536
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I can't believe how tough you are.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1537
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Anybody want to play a round of UNO?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1540
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Not tonight, man...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1542
msgid "Appo was truly wiped out. He didn't even move an inch."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1543
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hey stay up, don't leave me alone!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1546
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Are you a kid? Stupid brats who throw a tantrum and wake you when you're trying to sleep really do exist.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1547
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, sorry.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1550
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"See? I've got a visitor! It could be Pierre and Daigo!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1551
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Good for you. Go play with them.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1557
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"Good evening, Kazushi. Is my Ah-chan here?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1558
msgid "It was Fuusen."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1563
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Oh, hey Fuu-chan.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1564
msgid "Appo waved at her from under the covers. Fuusen came inside."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1567
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"You're like a giant baby sometimes.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1568
msgid "She sounded like a kind mother as she knelt next to Appo."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1571
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"You must be exhausted.\n"
"You're already half-asleep, aren't you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1572
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I am, Fuu-chan, let me sleep on your lap.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1575
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"You're so cute, but I can't do that. Haruma-kun's here too.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1576
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1579
msgid "They both gave me a look. It was hard to stay here."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1580
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Am I bothering you guys?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1583
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"Not at all. This is your room. Use it as you please.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1584
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Are you sure......?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1585
msgid "It definitely wasn't that kind of mood at all. I could hear voices from the audience all over the world shouting, \"Get the hell out right now!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1586
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I... think I'm going to take a walk.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1589
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Really? Well, take your time and enjoy the night air!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1592
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"Please do. I read a fortune that says good things will happen tomorrow if you walk for at least two hours.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1593
msgid ""
"Two hours!?\n"
"Don't tell me they're going to have sex here!?"
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1594
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"...I'll see you guys later.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1599
msgid ""
"{Appo & Fuusen}\n"
"\"Have fun!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1603
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I can't believe those two......Ah!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1605
msgid "The lights went out as soon as I left our room."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1606
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't tell me they're actually...Brrr!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1607
msgid "I nearly pictured the two of them doing it, and shivers raced down my spine. I'll stop thinking about it."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1608
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I'm such a loser.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1609
msgid ""
"I'm actually envious of Appo.\n"
"He's the only one with a girlfriend."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1610
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I don't know what to do by myself now...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1611
msgid "Maybe I should see how Daigo and Pierre are doing. Then again, I don't want them to know that I've been sexiled by Appo and Fuusen."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1612
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh man, I wish there was someone to comfort me...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1613
msgid "I wonder if there's a girl who'd be willing to talk to me..."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1614
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh yeah!\n"
"At times like this...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1624
msgid "Haruka, huh? I don't have to worry much around her after all."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1625
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Alright, I'll go see Haruka.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1628
msgid "Mizuki, huh? I thought she hated me at first, but now that our little misunderstanding has been cleared up, we're good friends."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1629
msgid "Once I got to know her, she was pretty laid-back, and easy to get along with."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1630
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"And with Mizuki, it won't turn into a sexy mood either.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1631
msgid "It's kind of lacking, but thanks to that, we could talk casually."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1632
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Alright, I'll have Mizuki help me kill some time.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1635
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, that's probably suitable.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1636
msgid "I can easily talk to Ran, and she'll probably welcome it."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1637
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Wait, considering the time, she might try and charge late night fees.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1638
msgid ".....................Whatever, might as well go."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1641
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"...Really?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1642
msgid "Why Natsume-chan? I hardly know anything about her."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1643
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I wonder why?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1644
msgid "I was curious about her. Since she made an appearance like that, it's only natural to be curious."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1645
msgid "That's not just it..."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1646
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, I might find out if I talk to her myself.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1647
msgid "Besides, Natsume-chan did tell me to come to her room. Mei-sensei said no, but I guess I'll sneak in."
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1650
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"If I see Mei-sensei, I'm sure she'll accompany me for a while.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02606:1651
msgid "At the very least she won't be cruel, which is reassuring."
msgstr ""
